---
title: Roasted Aubergine & Chickpeas with Pearl Barley Jumble and Feta
description: A delicious mix of roasted sweet potato, tomatoes and aubergine, crunchy chickpeas, nutty pearl barley and creamy feta, this bountiful bowl of goodness is the perfect thing to fill you up after a long day. Seasoned with Middle-Eastern inspired flavours like paprika and cumin, served with peppery rocket (a good source of calcium) and finished off with a squeeze of fresh lemon, this healthy but hearty dish is a real weeknight winner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-aubergine-spicy-chickpeas-0cc7fd92-cc8beb47.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/roasted-aubergine-spicy-chickpeas-5c6fdd4bc445fa0c35711d62-d60efb29.pdf
